'''cilium''' (''Plural:'' '''[[cilia]]''')
{{wikipedia}}

#(Biolgy) A hairlike [[organelle]] projecting from a [[eukaryotic]] [[cell]] (such as unicellular organism or one cell of a multicelled organism).  These structures serve either for [[locomotion]] by moving or as sensors.

